   Shakarishvili, Nana, Ilia State Univ, Inst Bot, Dept Plant Genet Resources, Tbilisi, Georgia.
   Osishvili, Liana, Natl Bot Garden, Dept Ecol Educ, Tbilisi, Georgia.},
